TOLEDO RECONCILED IN LATE 1996. 
 
12.  (C) SINCE THEN KARP HAS WORKED AS A MANAGER IN AN 
AGRICULTURE BANK.  THOUGH CREDITED WITH HELPING TOLEDO\'S 
CAMPAIGN BY USING HER KNOWLEDGE OF PERU AND FLUENT QUECHUA 
TO APPEAL TO VOTERS, SHE HAS COME UNDER ATTACK FROM THE 
YELLOW PRESS AND OTHERS FOR HER LIBERAL VIEWS AND STATUS AS 
A FOREIGNER.  SOURCES CLOSE TO TOLEDO CONFIRM THAT KARP 
URGED HER HUSBAND TO DON A HEADBAND AND LEAD PROTESTERS IN A 
MARCH ON THE PRESIDENTIAL PALACE AFTER THE POLLS CLOSED 
APRIL 9, A DECISION THAT MANY PERUVIAN OPINION MAKERS 
FOUND QUESTIONABLE. 
13.  (S) A FUJIMORI POLLSTER AND OTHER PRO-GOVERNMENT 
SOURCES HAVE CONVEYED TO CURRENT AND FORMER EMBOFFS THAT THE 
GOP HAS EVIDENCE OF DRUG (INCLUDING COCAINE) USE BY TOLEDO; 
JUST WHEN THE DRUG USE IS SUPPOSED TO HAVE OCCURRED IS 
UNCLEAR.  IT MAY HAVE BEEN DURING TOLEDO\'S STUDENT DAYS AT 
THE UNIVERSITY OF SAN FRANCISCO AND STANFORD 25-30 YEARS 
AGO.  THUS FAR, THERE IS NOTHING TO SUGGEST HE CONTINUED, 
BUT THIS ISSUE COULD PROVE EXPLOSIVE IN THE LEAD UP TO THE 
SECOND ROUND. 
 
------- 
COMMENT 
------- 
 
14. (S) THE FUJIMORI CAMP SEEMS INTENT ON MAKING CHARACTER A 
                          SECRET 
 
PAGE 03        LIMA  02475  03 OF 03  251229Z 
CENTRAL ISSUE IN THE SECOND ROUND (I.E., CONTINUE WITH SMEAR 
TACTICS), AS EVERYONE FROM VICE PRESIDENTIAL CANDIDATE 
TUDELA ON DOWN HAS FOUND REASONS NOT TO SUPPORT HUMAN RIGHTS 
OMBUDSMAN JORGE SANTISTEVAN\'S PROPOSAL FOR AN ELECTORAL CODE 
OF CONDUCT AND ETHICS TRIBUNAL. FUJIMORI\'S SUPPORTERS HAVE 
ALREADY PORTRAYED TOLEDO AS A RABBLE ROUSING DEMAGOGUE CUT 
IN THE MOLD OF ALAN GARCIA.  WE EXPECT PRO-GOVERNMENT 
JOURNALISTS TO EGG TOLEDO TO ISSUE AN ON-THE-RECORD DENIAL 
OF DRUG USE AND DOMESTIC VIOLENCE, FOLLOWED BY LEAKING OF 
WHATEVER EVIDENCE THE GOVERNMENT HAS.   FOR HIS PART, TOLEDO 
IS LIKELY TO REFUSE ANY COMMENT ON THE ALLEGATIONS.  WE 
SHOULD ALSO REFUSE COMMENT. 
 
